snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Digital Ange - Dennou Tenshi SS (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Digital Ange: Dennou Tenshi SS is an Adventure game, developed by Koga Game Factory and published by Tokuma Shoten, which was released in Japan in 1997.
